<h1>The list below is a list of your workout statistics!</h1>
<p>If you see an error, please visit the edit link.</p>


<h2>Type of workout:</h2>
<%=@workout.name%><br>
<h2>Body parts worked:</h2>
<%=@workout.muscle_group%><br>
<h2>Length of workout:</h2>
<%=@workout.duration%><br>
<h2>Amount of calories burnt!</h2>
<%=@workout.calories_burned%><br>

<label>Please review the options below:</label><br>
<% if @workout.user_id == current_user.id%>
<form action="/workouts/<%= @workout.id %>" method="post">
  <input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 15px;" onclick="window.location.href ='/workouts/<%=@workout.id%>';">Delete Workout</button><br>
  </form><br>
<button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 15px;" onclick="window.location.href ='/workouts/new';">New workout:</button><br>
<button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 15px;" onclick="window.location.href ='/workouts/<%=@workout.id%>/edit';">Edit Workout</button><br>

<%end%>